There is a new and exciting SIRI iOS Spotlight and TV App update for Classix! SIRI Support: You can now launch Classix movies and TV shows from SIRI. Just say a command like: Hey Siri show me The Lone Ranger and tap Open with Classix and it will launch the show right in the Classix app. Spotlight and Universal Search Support: You can now type Classix movies shows from your device s search spotlight and when you tap on the Classix show you want to watch you can then launch it right in the Classix app. TV App Support: You ll now find Classix movies shows within Apple s TV App browse around TV Show s and see if you can find some classics tap on the Classix show and it ll launch it within the Classix app and keep track of your progress if you want to finish it later.
